PREFIX dbpcat: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>
PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>

SELECT ?commonBroader
WHERE {
  ?concept1 skos:broader ?commonBroader OPTION (transitive, t_max(5), t_in(?concept1), t_out(?commonBroader), t_step("step_no") as ?dist1) .
  FILTER (?concept1 = dbpcat:RDF_data_access)
  ?concept2 skos:broader ?commonBroader OPTION (transitive, t_max(5), t_in(?concept2), t_out(?commonBroader), t_step("step_no") as ?dist2) .
  FILTER (?concept2 = dbpcat:Semantic_wiki_software)
}
ORDER BY ASC(?dist1   ?dist2)
LIMIT 1

PREFIX skos: <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> 

SELECT ?a ?b
WHERE {

}

PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX dbpedia-owl: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

select ?categorie ?broader
where {
?categorie skos:broader ?broader 
OPTION(TRANSITIVE, T_DISTINCT, t_in(?categorie), t_out(?broader), t_max(2), t_step('path_id') as ?path, t_step(?categorie) as ?route, t_step('step_no') AS ?jump, T_DIRECTION 2 )
}

OPTION(TRANSITIVE, T_DISTINCT, t_in(?categorie), t_out(?broader), t_max(2), t_step('path_id') as ?path, t_step(?categorie) as ?route, t_step('step_no') AS ?jump,
